    <text>
        <body>
            <div frus:doc-dateTime-max="1945-03-27T23:59:59-05:00"
                frus:doc-dateTime-min="1945-03-27T00:00:00-05:00" n="45"
                subtype="historical-document" type="document" xml:id="d45">
                <note rend="inline" type="source">893.48/3–2745: Telegram</note>
                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">The <gloss type="from">Acting Secretary of State</gloss> to
                        the Chargé in China</hi> (<persName type="to">
                        <hi rend="italic">Atcheson</hi>
                    </persName>)</head>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Washington</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1945-03-27">March 27,
                            1945</date>.</dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>505. An AP report Chungking dateline March 26 states that 20,000,000 persons in
                    northern Szechwan face famine because of drought and crop failure. Please
                    investigate and report.</p>
                <closer>
                    <signed>
                        <hi rend="smallcaps">Grew</hi>
                    </signed>
                </closer>
            </div>
        </body>
